### Get all authorities
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities

### Get an authority by DNI
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/10101015

### Search authorities by name
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/search?q=Juan

### Search authorities by zone
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities?zone=Centro

### Search authorities by name and filter by zone
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/search?q=Juan&zone=Centro

### Search authorities by name and filter by rank
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/search?q=Juan&rank=1

### Filter authorities by zone and rank (without name search)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/search?zone=Centro&rank=1

### Get bribes from an authority
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/10101015/bribes

### Get bribes from an authority with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/authorities/10101015/bribes?paid=true&minAmount=100&maxAmount=500&page=1&limit=5

